            "Details": "\"MechWarriors belong in the 'Mechs. Technicians belong in the Mech Bay. But you seem pretty knowledgeable about these things, and you've already pulled the schematics have the 'Mech in a harness. Explain to Yang what you were going for, and maybe he can finish what you started.\"\r\n\r\nLater that week, you catch [[TGT_MW,{TGT_MW.Callsign}]] in the hall.\r\n\r\n\"Chief Virtanen wanted me to pass along the good news. He investigated your suggestions and managed to turn that Locust into a 20 ton mace.  He's called it the [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[BaseDesc_Special_Mace_Locust],Locust Stick]].\"\r\n\r\n{TGT_MW.Callsign} basks in the glow of victory. \"I knew it would work! Soâ€¦ does that mean I'm riding out on the next contract? I feel like I should be the first to get to use it!\"",
